---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
const lastUpdated = "January 18, 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Dome"
  description="Privacy policy for Dome"
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">‚Üê Back to home</a>

      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>üîí Summary:</strong> Dome is 100% offline. Your data never
        leaves your device unless you choose to send it.
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>We do not collect any information.</strong> Dome is a
          fully offline application that stores all data locally on your
          device.
        </p>
        <p>
          Data you create (notes, resources, settings) is stored in:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>macOS:</strong> ~/Library/Application Support/Dome Pro/
          </li>
          <li><strong>Windows:</strong> %APPDATA%/Dome Pro/</li>
          <li><strong>Linux:</strong> ~/.config/Dome Pro/</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Third-Party Services (Optional)</h2>
        <p>
          If you choose to use AI features, the Application may connect to:
        </p>

        <h3>OpenAI</h3>
        <p>
          For embeddings (semantic search) and chat. Data sent may include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Text from your resources (to generate embeddings)</li>
          <li>Search queries</li>
          <li>Chat messages</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          See <a href="https://openai.com/privacy" target="_blank"
            >OpenAI‚Äôs privacy policy</a
          >.
        </p>

        <h3>Anthropic</h3>
        <p>
          For chat features. See the <a
            href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy"
            target="_blank">Anthropic privacy policy</a
          >.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Note:</strong> API keys are stored locally on your device and
          are never shared with us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>All your data is stored locally:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>SQLite database:</strong> Projects, resources, metadata
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Vector database (LanceDB):</strong> Embeddings for search
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>File system:</strong> PDFs, images, videos, audio
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You have full control over this data. You can export, back up, or
          delete it at any time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Security</h2>
        <p>
          Because your data stays on your device, security depends on the
          measures you apply to your operating system (password, disk
          encryption, etc.).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access all your data (it is on your device)</li>
          <li>Export your data at any time</li>
          <li>
            Delete your data completely by removing the application folder
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Any changes will be posted on this page. We recommend reviewing it
          periodically.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy-related questions, open an issue on the <a
            href="https://github.com/maxprain12/dome"
            target="_blank">GitHub repository</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 300px);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-fast);
  }
  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .highlight-box {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .highlight-box strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
